  skillDescription: "Summons a Sniper Gang Grunt as an Ally with ATK equal to your
    Base ATK, a WAIT of $WAIT, and a WAIT LIMIT of $WAITLIMIT (Current Wait: 50).
    \rThis Ally cannot be Attacked or individually targeted for Effects. This Ally
    will independently Attack the last Enemy you attacked on its turn. Lasts until
    the end of the battle, or until you die."
